00:04:37.800 --> 00:04:39.800
Our inevitable difficulties are aggravated by notions that offices are at heart really giant families,

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:45.000
that colleagues can be friends, that honesty is rewarded and that talent will win out.

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:50.500
Kindly sentimentality is in the end, just a disguised version of cruelty.

00:04:50.500 --> 00:04:57.300
It might be a lot simpler if, in dark moments, we could simply admit to what we know in our hearts:

00:04:57.300 --> 00:05:03.100
that it would obviously be a great deal better if we could be shot of the whole business of colleagues and

00:05:03.100 --> 00:05:09.700
could instead spend our days, as we used to do so well, on our own.

